==> By using findByXXX () methods we can retrieve the data based on no-prmary key columns also
==> When we write findByXXX method, JPA will construct query based on method name..

    Note: Method Naming convention is very important for findByXXX methods.....

==> Using findBy methods we can perform select operations only(retrieval). INSERT / UPDATE/ DELETE operations we con't do using findBy methods.

    Note: In findBy method syntax we will use entity variable names...


